{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "緊追猛趕", "storyInfo": "陳林二人再次出現在大螢幕上，然而此時她們已經落後領先部隊太多，她們趕得上嗎？\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6, "crossfade": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "水月選手在放棄了阻攔伏兵後，來到將陳林兩位選手掩埋的武器店廢墟之上，停留了一會兒後便不知所蹤。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們所有的攝影機和無人機都沒有找到他的位置。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而第一梯隊中，甜蜜夏日隊，已經最先抵達游泳檢查點。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一梯隊的其他隊伍也陸續穿過了游泳檢查點。", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們最關心的鼠膽龍威隊中，埃內斯托小弟為了殿後已經被打倒，我們的工作人員判斷他已經失去戰鬥能力了。", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳林兩位女俠此時卻依然沒有動靜。", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道真的萬事休矣了嗎？！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老陳，你不是吧，你不會倒在這種地方的對吧。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊小姐對比賽很在意呢。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_190_1#2"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡，她絕對是給陳押了大注，才在那念叨。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "認識這麼久了，這種比賽的輸贏，誰在乎啊。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "輸了又不代表就怎麼了，贏了也不能證明什麼。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒是希望她輸了，這樣我才好嘲笑她。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，艾雅法拉，來，我來給你試試這款面霜，我覺得一定適合你。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#7"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，謝謝。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_190_1#6"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然，又一聲轟鳴，從停留在埃內斯托武器店的鏡頭螢幕中傳來。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，這難道是......", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G02", "fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "pla